<P>A COMIC OPERA. AS PERFORMED AT THE <HI>THEATRE-ROYAL,</HI> IN COVENT-GARDEN.</P>
<P>Written by Captain JEPHSON.</P>
<P>LONDON: Printed for T. CADELL, in the Strand. M.DCC.LXXXV.</P>
